com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc80ed7x029ro.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Now%20it's%20like%20Ashes'%20-%20Starc%20on%20Ind%20vs%20Aus%20battle%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724221502000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112673046%2Cimgsize-30702.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fnow-its-right-on-par-with-ashes-mitchell-starc-on-india-vs-australia-for-border-gavaskar-trophy%2Farticleshow%2F112672574.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20upcoming%20year-end%20series%20has%20been%20expanded%20to%20five%20Tests%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20which%20makes%20the%20premier%20Australian%20fast%20bowler%20believe%20that%20it's%20now%20on%20equal%20footing%20with%20the%20Ashes%20series.%20India%20have%20won%20the%20Border%20Gavaskar%20for%20the%20last%20four%20editions%2C%20including%20two%20historic%20triumphs%20on%20the%20Australian%20soil.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jay%20Shah%20To%20Be%20Named%20ICC%20Chairman%2C%20Will%20Replace%20Greg%20Barclay%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20secretary%20Jay%20Shah%20is%20all%20set%20to%20replace%20the%20incumbent%20Greg%20Barclay%20as%20the%20new%20chairman%20of%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%2C%20sources%20have%20confirmed%20to%20NDTV.%20Barclay%20told%20ICC%20directors%2C%20including%20Cricket%20Australia's%20chair%20Mike%20Baird%2C%20that%20he%20has%20no%20intention%20of%20running%20for%20the%20post%2C%20for%20the%20third%20tirm%20during%20a%20video%20conference.%20His%20decision%20comes%20after%20being%20informed%20of%20Jay%20Shah's%20intentions%20to%20replace%20him%20in%20November.%20Shah%20has%20the%20backing%20of%20cricket%20boards%20from%20England%20and%20Australia%2C%20and%20hence%2C%20has%20the%20numbers%20to%20do%20be%20crowned%20the%20as%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20ICC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJagmohan%20Dalmiya%20(1997%20to%20200)%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar%20(2010-2012)%20are%20the%20only%20two%20Indians%20who%20have%20held%20the%20position%20of%20ICC's%20chief%20in%20the%20past.%20Shah%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20son%20of%20India's%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20will%20become%20the%20third%20to%20do%20so%20when%20he%20officially%20replaces%20Barclay%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BICC%20chair%20Greg%20Barclay%20confirmed%20to%20the%20board%20that%20he%20will%20not%20stand%20for%20a%20third%20term%20and%20will%20step%20down%20from%20the%20post%20when%20his%20current%20tenure%20finishes%20at%20the%20end%20of%20November.%20Barclay%20was%20appointed%20as%20the%20independent%20ICC%20chair%20in%20November%202020%2C%20before%20being%20re-elected%20in%202022%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20ICC%20spokesperson%20told%20The%20Age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCurrent%20directors%20are%20now%20required%20to%20put%20forward%20nominations%20for%20the%20next%20chair%20by%2027%20August%202024%20and%20if%20there%20is%20more%20than%20one%20candidate%2C%20an%20election%20will%20be%20held%20with%20the%20term%20of%20the%20new%20chair%20commencing%20on%201%20December%202024.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20ICC%20rules%2C%20the%20chairman's%20election%20comprises%20of%2016%20votes%20and%20now%20a%20simple%20majority%20of%20nine%20votes%20is%20required%20(51%25)%20for%20the%20winner.%20Earlier%2C%20to%20become%20the%20chairman%2C%20the%20incumbent%20needed%20to%20have%20two-third%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20enjoys%20a%20lot%20of%20goodwill%20with%20most%20of%20the%2016%20voting%20members.%20Currently%2C%20Shah%20has%20another%20one%20year%20left%20as%20the%20BCCI%20secretary%20before%20going%20on%20a%20mandatory%20cooling%20off%20period%20of%20three%20years%20from%20October%2C%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20BCCI%20constitution%20appr