om%20Mr%20Niccol's%20last%20working%20place.%20But%20the%20Mexican%20fast%20food%20chain%20moved%20its%20headquarters%20from%20Denver%20to%20California%20three%20months%20after%20he%20was%20appointed%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBrian's%20primary%20office%20and%20a%20majority%20of%20his%20time%20will%20be%20spent%20in%20our%20Seattle%20Support%20Center%20or%20out%20visiting%20partners%20and%20customers%20in%20our%20stores%2C%20roasteries%2C%20roasting%20facilities%20and%20offices%20around%20the%20world.%20His%20schedule%20will%20exceed%20the%20hybrid%20work%20guidelines%20and%20workplace%20expectations%20we%20have%20for%20all%20partners%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20company%20spokesperson%20told%20CNBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20comfortable%20terms%20for%20employment%20are%20common%20for%20high-ranking%20executives%20who%20have%20immense%20bargaining%20power%20compared%20to%20the%20average%20employee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHillary%20Super%20of%20singer%20Rihanna's%20lingerie%20brand%20Fenty%20x%20Savage%20was%20given%20a%20s%20similar%20concession%20when%20Victoria's%20Secret%20made%20her%20its%20new%20CEO.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20will%20work%20from%20the%20firm's%20New%20York%20City%20offices%20instead%20of%20its%20headquarters%20near%20Columbus%2C%20Ohio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20is%20not%20the%20case%20for%20all%20CEOs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmazon's%20Andy%20Jassy%20and%20JPMorgan%20Chase's%20Jamie%20Dimon%20are%20pitching%20hard%20to%20bring%20back%20work-from-office%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20behind%20Mr%20Niccol's%20unusual%20arrangement%20at%20Starbucks%20is%20underscored%20by%20the%20coffee%20giant's%20falling%20sales.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20US%20and%20China%2C%20Starbucks'%20two%20largest%20markets%2C%20sales%20have%20dropped%20this%20year%20under%20its%20current%20CEO%20Laxman%20Narasimhan's%20tenure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Niccol%20is%20a%20star%20candidate%20for%20the%20top%20post%20as%20he%20has%20a%20strong