0partnerships%20in%20a%20Fintech%20company.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20150-year-old%20pine%20tree%20toppled%20and%20fell%20through%20my%20roof%20last%20April%2C%20my%20family%20of%20four%20had%20to%20relocate%20temporarily%20while%20it%20got%20fixed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20had%20to%20find%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ea%20place%20where%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewe%20could%20both%20work%20and%20have%20childcare%20for%20our%20two%20kids%2C%20who%20were%206%20months%20old%20and%204%20at%20the%20time.%20We%20also%20saw%20it%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20explore%20somewhere%20new.%20We%20considered%20New%20York%20and%20San%20Francisco%2C%20but%20then%20thought%20this%20could%20be%20a%20once-in-a-lifetime%20chance%20to%20pick%20up%20and%20go%20somewhere%20farther%2C%20and%20decided%20on%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-visiting-dubai-for-first-time-with-family-kids-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDubai.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eworked%20in%20Dubai%20in%202013%20and%20enjoyed%20my%20time%20there.%20My%20husband%20is%20an%20entrepreneur%20and%20had%20opportunities%20to%20work%20there.%20So%2C%20we%20thought%3A%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-move-family-kids-to-dubai-similarities-to-america-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhy%20don't%20we%20just%20go%20to%20Dubai%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20trip%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20three%20weeks%20%E2%80%94%20but%20that%20turned%20into%20eight%2C%20and%20then%2010.%20My%20husband%20started%20work%20in%20his%20startup%20in%20Dubai%20while%20I%20shuttled%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Dubai%2C%20applied%20for%20jobs%2C%20and%20prepared%20our%20house%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20to%20be%20rented.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%20this%20year%2C%20I%20found%20a%20job%20in%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-first-time-visitors-dubai-from-locals-live-there-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDubai%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20we%20were%20able%20to%20relocate%20there%C2%A0permanently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22661fa057-88fd-4c9a-aa0c-171e89249ee9%5C%22%3EI%20like%20who%20I%20am%20as%20a%20mother%20in%20Dubai%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20mother%20in%20the%20US%2C%20I%20didn't%20have%20much%20support.%20I%20worked%2C%20did%20the%20laundry%2C%20and%20ran%20around%20for%20my%20children's%20activities.%20I%20didn't%20have%20that%20much%20quality%20time%20left%20over%20for%20my%20kids%20because%20I%20ran%20the%20household%20and%20worked%20full-time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdubai-tax-safety-security-top-cities-workation-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDubai%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20however%2C%20the%20culture%20is%20built%20around%20quality%20time%20with%20your%20family.%20When%20I%20come%20home%20from%20work%2C%20our%20part-time%20nanny%2C%20who%20we%20pay%204%2C000%20AED%2C%20or%20%241%2C089%20a%20month%2C%20has%20already%20done%20the%20laundry%2C%20cooked%20the%20food%2C%20and%20bathed%20the%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%206%20p.m.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI'm%20done%20with%20work.%20There's%20no%20expectation%20that%20I'll%20be%20checking%20my%20emails.%20So%20when%20I%20come%20to%20my%20children%2C%20they're%20not%20getting%20yelled%20at%20because%20they%20are%20not%20getting%20a%20distracted%20parent.%20They're%20getting%20the%20best%20version%20of%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fcad7525-9016-41b8-ae75-e434c1aba784%5C%22%3EI%20am%20more%20relaxed%20here%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20we%20were%20often%20overscheduled.%20I%20knew%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethree%20or%20four%20weeks%20in%20advance%20what%20we%20would%20be%20doing%20every%20single%20weekend%20%E2%80%94%20spontaneity%20died%20at%20the%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20Dubai%2C%20we%20don't%20stress%20over%20booking%20restaurant%20reservations%20or%20worry%20about%20a%20place%20being%20too%20crowded.%20We%20figure%20it%20out%20as%20we%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20this%2C%20I%20spend%20more%20quality%20time%20with%20my%20spouse%2C%20new%20friends%2C%20and%20children.%20My%20weekends%20are%20truly%20relaxing.%20When%20I%20return%20to%20work%20on%20Mondays%2C%20I%20am%20the%20best%20version%20of%20myself%20in%20the%20corporate%20setting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20work%2C%20face-to-face%20relationships%20are%20valued.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20lines%20between%20professional%20and%20personal%20can%20be%20slightly%20blurred.%20A%20lot%20of%20networking%20is%20done%20via%20WhatsApp.%20And%20so%2C%20you%20can%20set%20up%20a%20meeting%2C%20and%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20send%20memes%20or%20talk%20about%20traveling.%20There's%20no%20facade%20that%20everyone%20has%20to%20be%20very%20serious%20all%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226145940e-e07f-4730-8b63-d418df226799%5C%22%3EIt's%20also%20easier%20to%20make%20friends%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20group%20of%20people%20sitting%20around%20a%20table%20and%20playing%20board%20games.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c2fb0f5da406397bf6c93f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAli%20celebrated%20her%20first%20Eid%20holiday%20in%20Dubai%20with%20her%20friends.%3Cp%3EKiran%20Ali%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMaking%20friends%20was%20much%20harder%20back%20in%20the%20US%2C%20as%20people%20mostly%20had%20their%20groups%20of%20friends%20from%20school%20and%20were%20not%20inclined%20to%20include%20new%20friends.%20Because%20everything%20was%20so%20scheduled%20in%20the%20US%2C%20finding%20someone%20to%20watch%20our%20kids%20and%20take%20time%20for%20ourselves%20was%20also%20more%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20making%20friends%20has%20never%20been%20a%20concern%20in%20Dubai.%20Living%20in%20an%20expat%20city%2C%20where%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dsc.gov.ae%2Fen-us%2FThemes%2FPages%2FPopulation-and-Vital-Statistics.aspx%3FTheme%3D42%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E92%25%20of%20its%203%2C655%2C000-person%20population%20is%20non-Emirati%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20everyone's%20very%20open%20to%20meeting.%20Once%20you're%20plugged%20into%20one%20network%2C%20you'll%20also%20meet%20all%20the%20other%20people%20there.%20And%20there%20are%20so%20many%20interesting%20and%20new%20people%20to%20meet%20here%20with%20different%20perspectives%20than%20we're%20used%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c24c999c-1ac9-4532-8347-f81946a8a6c9%5C%22%3EWe%20travel%20more%20as%20a%20family%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20we%20moved%20to%20Dubai%2C%20we%20were%20already%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eavid%20travelers.%20But%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdubai-economic-jewel-of-the-middle-east-gulf-neighbors-saudi-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDubai%20being%20a%20global%20hub%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20travel%20more%20now.%20Many%20affordable%20destinations%2C%20such%20as%20Kazakistan%20or%20Beirut%2C%20are%20within%20a%20five-hour%20flight.%20These%20vacation%20destinations%20were%20just%20out%20of%20reach%20when%20we%20lived%20in%20the%20US%20because%20of%20the%20cost%20and%20length%20of%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20decade%20since%20I%20last%20lived%20here%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-know-before-traveling-to-dubai-uae-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDubai%20has%20expanded%20its%20footprint%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Now%2C%20you%20can%20find%20people%20from%20all%20over%20the%20world%20and%20eat%20all%20different%20cuisines%20%E2%80%94%20it%20truly%20is%20a%20cosmopolitan%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverything%20here%20is%20also%20designed%20to%20make%20life%20easier.%20Anything%20from%20anywhere%20can%20be%20sent%20to%20your%20home%20in%2015%20minutes%20if%20you%20need%20something%20delivered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20we%20plan%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20US%20to%20visit%20every%20summer%2C%20but%20we'll%20continue%20living%20here%20as%20long%20as%20Dubai%20will%20have%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20just%20weird%20to%20think%20about%20how%20one%20freak%20accident%20changed%20the%20rest%20of%20our%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20about%20moving%20abroad%20that%20you%20want%20to%20share%3F%20Get%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20reporter%2C%20Erin%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aeliam%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eeliam%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-mom-expat-raising-kids-dubai-better-mother-relocation-uae-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724203060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c3f8531aa2ac29ee325c9f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-mom-expat-raising-kids-dubai-better-mother-relocation-uae-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kiran%20Ali%2C%20a%20mom%20of%20two%2C%20enjoys%20the%20quality%20of%20life%20and%20the%20culture%20in%20Dubai.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22eliam%40insider.com%20(Erin%20Liam)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A345%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-mom-expat-raising-kids-dubai-better-mother-relocation-uae-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20conducts%20'super%20unscientific'%20poll%20on%20X%3A%20Trump%20vs%20Harris%20%E2%80%94%20Results%20so%20far%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724202884000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2F