s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20being%20sworn%20into%20office%2C%20Ocasio-Cortez%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falexandria-ocasio-cortez-joins-climate-change-protest-outside-of-pelosi-office-2018-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejoined%20climate%20change%20activists%3C%2Fa%3E%20protesting%20outside%20of%20then-House%20Democratic%20leader%20Nancy%20Pelosi's%20Capitol%20Hill%20office%20in%20November%202018%2C%20an%20early%20sign%20that%20she%20would%20not%20be%20deferential%20to%20leadership%20on%20the%20key%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20observers%2C%20all%20signs%20pointed%20to%20a%20perpetual%20ideological%20tussle%20between%20Ocasio-Cortez%20and%20top%20Democrats.%20But%20along%20the%20way%2C%20she's%20broadened%20her%20appeal%20within%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZQYrbcO1Qu0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20full%20display%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20first%20night%20of%20the%20Democratic%20National%20Convention%20in%20Chicago%2C%20when%20Ocasio-Cortez%20was%20not%20only%20given%20a%20prime%20speaking%20slot%20but%20received%20rave%20reviews%20by%20many%20for%20her%20defense%20of%20the%20party's%20values%20and%20her%20strong%20backing%20of%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris'%20presidential%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22776b2fcd-c9cc-4077-af1d-d676cc8838b2%5C%22%3EFrom%20progressive%20newbie%20to%20Democratic%20insider%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20slots%20at%20national%20conventions%20are%20perfect%20opportunities%20for%20up-and-coming%20politicians%20to%20get%20face%20time%20with%20the%20party%20faithful%20and%20tap%20into%20the%20sort%20of%20connections%20that%20can%20pay%20dividends%20down%20the%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBut%20this%20is%20AOC.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20congresswoman%20became%20a%20household%20name%20after%20winning%20her%20highly%20consequential%20primary%20race%20eight%20years%20ago.%20But%20while%20Ocasio-Cortez's%20ideology%20has%20largely%20stayed%20intact%20%E2%80%94%20notably%20on%20backing%20student-loan%20debt%20relief%2C%20continued%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Focasio-cortez.house.gov%2Fmedia%2Fpress-releases%2Focasio-cortez-sanders-ramirez-reintroduce-green-new-deal-public-housing-act%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupport%20for%20a%20Green%20New%20Deal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20push%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20Gaza%20%E2%80%94%20a%20lot%20has%20also%20changed%20since%20she%20began%20her%20career%20on%20Capitol%20Hill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOcasio-Cortez%20is%20now%20the%20vice%20ranking%20member%2C%20or%20the%20No.%202%20Democrat%2C%20on%20the%20House%20Oversight%20Committee%2C%20one%20of%20the%20highest-profile%20panels%20in%20the%20lower%20chamber.%20It%20is%20on%20this%20committee%20where%20the%20congresswoman%20has%20been%20able%20to%20flex%20her%20own%20leadership%20skills%20while%20also%20working%20with%20Republican%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20Monday%2C%20Ocasio-Cortez%20%E2%80%94%20who%20became%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faoc-biden-progressives-outreach-democratic-party-sanders-2024-election-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estrong%20ally%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20early%20on%20in%20his%20administration%20%E2%80%94%20gave%20a%20speech%20that%20could%20appeal%20to%20Democrats%20across%20the%20ideological%20spectrum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEver%20since%20I%20got%20elected%2C%20Republicans%20have%20attacked%20me%20by%20saying%20that%20I%20should%20go%20back%20to%20bartending%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20let%20me%20tell%20you%2C%20I'm%20happy%20to%20any%20day%20of%20the%20week%20because%20there%20is%20nothing%20wrong%20with%20working%20for%20a%20living.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOcasio-Cortez's%20message%20leaned%20into%20the%20sort%20of%20economic%20populism%20that%20both%20Harris%20and%20vice-presidential%20candidate%20Tim%20Walz%20will%20need%20to%20win%20across%20the%20Upper%20Midwest%20and%20in%20states%20like%20Nevada%20and%20Pennsylvania.%20And%20the%20crowd%20ate%20up%20the%20congresswoman's%20words.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220b8abf1d-b6c7-41ae-9c58-bb6455a08b57%5C%22%3EThe%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOcasio-Cortez's%20speech%20was%20seemingly%20a%20declaration%20to%20any%20remaining%20Democratic%20skeptics%20that%20she's%20a%20vital%20voice%20within%20the%20party%20%E2%80%94%20and%20not%20the%20fringe%20figure%20that%20critics%20have%20sought%20to%20depict%20her%20as%20since%20joining%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20some%20political%20setbacks%2C%20including%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fmeet-the-press%2Fmeetthepressblog%2Focasio-cortez-backs-democratic-campaign-leaders-primary-challenger-rcna32356%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2022%20support%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20progressive%20New%20York%20state%20Sen.%20Alessandra%20Biaggi%20over%20then-incumbent%20Rep.%20Sean%20Patrick%20Maloney%20in%20the%20Democratic%20primary%20for%20New%20York's%20swingy%2017th%20congressional%20district.%20(Biaggi%20lost%20the%20primary%20and%20Maloney%20was%20defeated%20in%20the%20general%20election%20by%20now-Republican%20Rep.%20Mike%20Lawler.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20hasn't%20impacted%20Ocasio-Cortez%20being%20a%20draw%20for%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Frep-alexandria-ocasio-cortez-primetime-speech_n_66c3ead6e4b0802831f038bf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Huffington%20Post%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Ocasio-Cortez%20didn't%20seek%20out%20the%20convention%20speaking%20slot%2C%20but%20was%20contacted%20by%20convention%20organizers%20about%20making%20an%20appearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20a%20move%20shows%20that%20Ocasio-Cortez's%20appeal%2C%20especially%20among%20the%20young%20voters%20that%20Harris%20and%20Walz%20will%20need%20to%20win%20in%20November%2C%20has%20not%20gone%20unnoticed%20by%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20judging%20by%20the%20energetic%20reception%20that%20the%20congresswoman%20received%20as%20she%20walked%20offstage%2C%20her%20star%20will%20likely%20continue%20to%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faoc-democratic-national-convention-speech-political-evolution-progressives-mainstream-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724184901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c4f5241aa2ac29ee32a89e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faoc-democratic-national-convention-speech-political-evolution-progressives-mainstream-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rep.%20Alexandria%20Ocasio-Cortez%2C%20once%20seen%20as%20an%20insurgent%20looking%20to%20disrupt%20the%20Democratic%20Party%2C%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20key%20surrogate%20for%20VP%20Kamala%20Harris.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(John%20L.%20Dorman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A364%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faoc-democratic-national-convention-speech-political-evolution-progressives-mainstream-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hulk%20Hogan%20jokes%20about%20body%20slamming%20Kamala%20Harris%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724184539000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F2984%2Flive%2F51b62b20-5f20-11ef-aca5-6ffe5d06c346.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc4gzjzj989zo%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20former%20wrestler%2C%20who%20supports%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20also%20made%20comments%20about%20the%20vice-president's%20racial%20identity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A129%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc4gzjzj989zo%22%2