it%20alone%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20a%20close%20associate%20of%20the%20accused%20was%20captured%20sprinting%20and%20reaching%20the%20CBI%20Special%20Crime%20Branch%20office%20in%20Kolkata%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20the%20trainee%20doctor%20have%20sparked%20widespread%20outrage%20and%20protests%20across%20various%20cities%2C%20with%20calls%20for%20justice%20and%20punishment%20for%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20taken%20suo-motu%20cognizance%20of%20the%20case%2C%20with%20a%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20scheduled%20to%20hear%20it%20on%20August%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20has%20received%20permission%20to%20conduct%20a%20polygraph%20test%20on%20the%20arrested%20accused%2C%20CBI%20sources%20said%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2018%2C%20the%20CBI%20team%20examined%20and%20conducted%203D%20laser%20mapping%20in%20the%20emergency%20ward%20of%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20in%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWest%20Bengal%20government%20has%20constituted%20a%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20(SIT)%20to%20conduct%20an%20enquiry%2Finvestigation%20into%20the%20allegations%20of%20financial%20irregularities%20in%20R%20G%20Kar%20Hospital%20during%20the%20period%20between%20January%202021%20and%20till%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724178120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F2fiichd_kolkata-doctor-rape-accused_625x300_12_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhe-caused-his-wife-a-miscarriage-claims-mother-in-law-of-kolkata-horror-accused-6381169%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kolkata%20rape%20and%20murd