%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frg-kar-rape-murder-bengal-governor-cv-ananda-bose-dials-rg-kar-doctors-parents-seeks-meeting-6381091%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bengal%20Governor%20CV%20Ananda%20Bose%2C%20who%20has%20shredded%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government%20repeatedly%20over%20the%20young%20doctor's%20rape%20and%20murder%2C%20spoke%20to%20her%20parents%20today%2C%20assuring%20them%20that%20he%20would%20make%20every%20effort%20to%20get%20them%20justice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frg-kar-rape-murder-bengal-governor-cv-ananda-bose-dials-rg-kar-doctors-parents-seeks-meeting-6381091%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThough%20Well%20Intentioned...%26quot%3B%3A%20Doctors'%20Body%20On%20Supreme%20Court%20Directive%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court's%20appeal%20that%20the%20doctors%20return%20to%20work%20notwithstanding%2C%20the%20protesting%20doctors%20of%20the%20country%20are%20not%20ready%20to%20relent.%20The%20court%2C%20which%20initiated%20a%20hearing%20on%20the%20massive%20row%20today%2C%20had%20tried%20to%20balance%20security%20of%20doctors%20with%20patient%20care%2C%20calling%20for%20a%20national%20protocol%20for%20safety%20at%20workplaces.%20But%20the%20doctors%20made%20their%20position%20clear.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20doctors'%20bodies%20--%20the%20All-India%20Residents%20and%20Junior%20Doctors'%20Joint%20Action%20Forum%20--%20has%20not%20minced%20words.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Supreme%20Court's%20directive%20for%20increased%20security%20at%20hospitals%2C%20while%20well-intentioned%2C%20does%20not%20address%20the%20core%20problems%20plaguing%20our%20healthcare%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20a%20communique%20from%20the%20Forum.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20real%20issue%20is%20a%20public%20healthcare%20system%20that%20has%20been%20systematically%