0Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%2C%20who%20led%20the%20three-judge%20bench%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20we%20decided%20to%20take%20suo%20motu%20though%20High%20Court%20was%20hearing%20it%20because%20this%20is%20not%20just%20a%20case%20of%20a%20horrific%20murder%20in%20the%20Kolkata%20hospital...but%20this%20is%20about%20systemic%20issue%20about%20safety%20of%20doctors%20across%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judges%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BSince%20the%20court%20is%20considering%20matters%20related%20to%20the%20safety%20and%20welfare%20of%20all%20doctors%2C%20we%20request%20those%20doctors%20who%20are%20currently%20away%20from%20work%20to%20resume%20their%20duties%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%20The%20absence%20of%20doctors%20affects%20the%20section%20of%20society%20that%20needs%20medical%20care.%20Doctors%20and%20medical%20professionals%20can%20be%20assured%20that%20their%20concerns%20are%20being%20addressed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20horrific%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20the%2031-year-old%20doctor%20at%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%2C%20the%20court%20spared%20none%20of%20the%20authorities%20-%20the%20hospital%2C%20the%20police%20or%20the%20state%20government.%20The%20top%20court%20has%20sought%20a%20status%20report%20from%20the%20investigating%20agency%20CBI%20on%20Thursday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20underscored%20the%20need%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bnational%20protocol%20for%20safe%20conditions%20of%20work%26quot%3B.%20Such%20a%20protocol%2C%20it%20said%2C%20has%20to%20be%20enforced%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724176800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F56q75jmg_kolkatadoctor7_625x300_19_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthough-well-intentioned-doctors-body-on-supreme-court-directive-6381063%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court's%20appeal%20that%20the%2