consider%20India's%20request%20to%20extradite%20controversial%20Islamic%20preacher%20Zakir%20Naik%20if%20it%20provides%20evidence%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20an%20interactive%20session%20at%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20World%20Affairs%2C%20Mr%20Ibrahim%20also%20said%20that%20the%20issue%20shouldn't%20deter%20the%20two%20countries%20from%20enhancing%20bilateral%20relations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20specific%20question%2C%20he%20said%20the%20issue%20was%20not%20raised%20by%20the%20Indian%20side%20during%20Tuesday's%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZakir%20Naik%20is%20wanted%20by%20the%20Indian%20authorities%20for%20alleged%20money%20laundering%20and%20inciting%20extremism%20through%20hate%20speeches.%20He%20left%20India%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Islamic%20preacher%20was%20granted%20permanent%20residency%20in%20Malaysia%20by%20the%20previous%20government%20led%20by%20Mahathir%20Mohamed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirstly%2C%20it%20was%20not%20raised%20by%20the%20(Indian%20side)%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20(Narendra%20Modi)%20did%20raise%20it%20much%20earlier%2C%20some%20years%20back...%20But%20the%20issue%20is%20I%20am%20not%20talking%20about%20one%20person%2C%20I%20am%20talking%20about%20the%20sentiment%20of%20extremism%2C%20of%20a%20compelling%20case%20and%20evidence%20that%20suggest%20the%20atrocities%20committed%20by%20an%20individual%20or%20group%20or%20faction%20or%20parties%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ibrahim%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Malaysian%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20his%20government%20is%20%26quot%3Bopen%20to%20any%20ideas%20and%20evidence%20submitted%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20not%20condone%20terrorism...%20We%20have%20been%20tough%20and%20we%20have%20been%20working%20together%20with%20India%20on%20many%20of%20these%20issues%2C%20against%20terrorism.%20But%20I%20don't%20think%20this%20one%20case%20should%20deter%20us%20from%20further%20collaboration%20and%20enhancing%20our%20bilateral%20cooperation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Malaysian%20Prime%20Minister%20began%20his%20three-day%20visit%20to%20India%20last%20night%20in%20his%20first%20trip%20to%20the%20country%20after%20becoming%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ibrahim%20also%20criticised%20Israel's%20military%20actions%20in%20Gaza%20and%20described%20the%20overall%20situation%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bsheer%20hypocrisy%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20West.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20atrocities%20of%20Israeli%20forces%20in%20Gaza%20that's%20real%2C%20killing%2040%2C000%20people.%20That%20is%20an%20atrocity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20must%20give%20a%20very%20clear%20message%20that%20this%20hypocrisy%20must%20end.%20You%20can't%20talk%20about%20genocide%20in%20Ukraine%20because%20of%20the%20bombing%20of%20some%20villages%2C%20and%2040%2C000%20people%20killed%20(in%20Gaza%20as)%20the%20impact%20of%20war%20and%20you%20can%20condone%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20response%20to%20a%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20shocking%20and%20I%20call%20it%20sheer%20hypocrisy.%20It%20is%20long-standing%20but%20it%20has%20to%20end%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20matter%20whether%20the%20victims%20are%20Muslims%20or%20Christians%20or%20Hindus%20or%20Buddhists%20or%20whatever.%20They%20are%20human%20beings%20and%20in%20this%20age%20for%20us%20(to%20say)%20that%20'I%20am%20sorry%2C%20nothing%20can%20be%20done'%2C%20is%20atrocious%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724176200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-08%2Fsqu1ss1g_zakir-naik_625x300_20_August_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmalaysia-indicates-that-indias-request-on-zakir-naik-can-be-considered-if-evidence-provided-6380844%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Malaysian%20Prime%20Minister%20Anwar%20Ibrahim%20on%20Tuesday%20indicated%20that%20his%20government%20may%20co