n%20a%20row%2C%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20which%20has%20taken%20over%20the%20case%20questioned%20Anup%20Dutta%2C%20an%20assistant%20sub-inspector%20and%20member%20of%20the%20city%20police%20welfare%20board.%20Mr%20Dutta's%20proximity%20to%20Sanjoy%20Roy%20is%20suspected%20to%20have%20led%20CBI%20officers%20to%20understand%20how%20Sanjoy%20Roy%20could%20have%20had%20free%20access%20to%20police%20barracks%20where%20he%20stayed%2C%20and%20within%20an%20institution%20like%20RG%20Kar%20Hospital%20where%20he%20could%20move%20around%20freely%20at%20all%20times%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20has%20reportedly%20accessed%20multiple%20photographs%20showing%20Dutta%20and%20Roy%20together%2C%20prompting%20them%20to%20dig%20out%20further%20details%20on%20the%20arrested%20man%20from%20the%20officer.%20Dutta%2C%20however%2C%20was%20seen%20sprinting%20towards%20the%20CBI%20office%20to%20avoid%20reporters%20when%20they%20asked%20him%20how%20long%20he%20knew%20the%20accused%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four-member%20state%20SIT%20spoke%20to%20former%20deputy%20superintendent%20of%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%2C%20Dr%20Akhtar%20Ali%2C%20the%20whistleblower%20and%20first%20complainant%20against%20financial%20irregularities%20against%20Sandip%20Ghosh%2C%20at%20the%20premises%20of%20Swasthya%20Bhawan%2C%20the%20state%20health%20department%20headquarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724172240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F2fiichd_kolkata-doctor-rape-accused_625x300_12_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkolkata-news%2Fkey-suspect-sanjay-roy-in-kolkata-doctor-rape-murder-case-went-to-red-light-area-cops-6380576%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20accused%20in%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20case%20of%20a%2031-year-old%20junior%20doctor%20in%20Kolkata%20had%20gone%20to%20two%20brothels%20in%20the%20city%20the%20night%20he%20committed%20the%20crime%2C%20the%20Kolkata%20Police%2