ood%20dream%20of%20swimming%20the%20English%20Channel.%20Despite%20facing%20physical%2C%20mental%2C%20and%20logistical%20challenges%2C%20here%E2%80%99s%20how%20she%20successfully%20completed%20the%2033-kilometre%20swim.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F361675%2Fnashik-swimmer-tanvi-deore-swam-across-english-channel-dover-france-open-water-swimming-champion%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20World%20Beyond%20Concrete%3A%205%20Construction%20Materials%20India%20is%20Using%20to%20Make%20Sustainable%20Homes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMud%20is%20%3Cem%3Ekaccha%20%3C%2Fem%3E(raw).%E2%80%9D%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSustainable%20architecture%20isn%E2%80%99t%20pretty.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArchitect%20Guruprasad%20Rane%20of%20the%20firm%20%E2%80%98Bhoomija%E2%80%99%20in%20Kerala%20would%20often%20hear%20some%20of%20these%20opinions%20being%20shared%20by%20his%20clients%20who%20wanted%20a%20new%20space%20built%20for%20them.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20now%20that%20is%20slowly%20changing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CClients%20these%20days%20are%20open%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F224900%2Fmumbai-architect-sustainable-homes-solar-air-conditioning-eco-friendly-cheap-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esustainable%20alternatives%20of%20construction%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20many%20cases%2C%20clients%20have%20approached%20us%20with%20a%20conventional%20cement%20design%20in%20mind.%20But%20we%20have%20introduced%20them%20to%20cob%2C%20soil%20and%20other%20materials%20that%20could%20work%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20architect%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20tune%20with%20this%2C%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20sat%20down%20with%20a%20bunch%20of%20architects%20who%20disproved%20the%20belief%20that%20cement%20is%20the%20only%20material%20suitable%20for%20construction.%20They%20believe%20it%20is%20time%20to%20do%20away%20with%20such%20ideals%20and%20make%20way%20for%20more%20planet-friendly%20perspectives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20architects%20in%20this%20piece%20converge%20on%20a%20verdict%20that%20responsible%20design%20and%20great%20aesthetics%20can%20indeed%20go%20hand-in-hand.%20Keeping%20conscious%20design%20at%20the%20fore%2C%20they%20are%20building%20a%20new%20India%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20is%20in%20tune%20with%20sustainability.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20deep-dived%20into%20their%20projects%20and%20understood%20the%20ethos%20behind%20each%20material%20used.%20Here%20are%20five%20that%20impressed%20us%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Rammed%20earth%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20residence%20of%20Dr%20Achutshankar%20in%20Karyavattom%2C%20Kerala%2C%20always%20draws%20two%20glances%20from%20any%20onlooker.%20The%20first%20is%20because%20of%20its%20beautiful%2C%20rust-coloured%20exterior%20that%20perfectly%20compliments%20the%20mud%20on%20which%20it%20stands%2C%20and%20the%20second%20is%20because%20people%20can%20hardly%20believe%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F335976%2Fmumbai-sustainable-home-ecofriendly-mud-architecture-geeli-mitti-ngo-lakhichand-jain%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estructure%20is%20built%20out%20of%20soil%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStanding%20proud%20of%20their%20creation%20are%20architect%20duo%20Guruprasad%20Rane%20and%20Manasi%20Puliyappatta%2C%20the%20brains%20behind%20the%20sustainable%20architecture%20firm%20%E2%80%98Bhoomija%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20use%20of%20rammed%20earth%20in%20the%20construction%2C%20Rane%20notes%20that%20it%20isn%E2%80%99t%20something%20novel.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20usage%20dates%20back%20to%