oints-expressway-karnal-haveli-amrik-sukhdev-azad-hind-dhaba%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Born%20With%20Spina%20Bifida%2C%20Comedian%20Sweta%20Mantrii%20Uses%20Humour%20To%20Fight%20for%20Inclusive%20Public%20Spaces%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20while%20recovering%20from%20a%20fracture%20and%20binge-watching%20stand-up%20comedy%20on%20YouTube%2C%20Sweta%20Mantrii%20had%20a%20revelation%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20witty%20too.%20Why%20not%20merge%20that%20with%20comedy%20about%20disability%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20sparked%20her%20journey%20into%20using%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F137498%2Fnortheast-india-abhineet-mishra-stereotype%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehumour%20as%20a%20tool%20for%20change%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESweta%2C%20now%2036%2C%20was%20born%20with%20spina%20bifida%20%E2%80%94%20a%20condition%20where%20the%20spine%20and%20spinal%20cord%20don%E2%80%99t%20develop%20properly%2C%20leaving%20a%20gap%20in%20the%20spine.%20Just%20before%20starting%20school%2C%20she%20underwent%20surgery%20and%20physiotherapy%2C%20which%20enabled%20her%20to%20walk%20using%20crutches.%20Women%20with%20this%20condition%20typically%20reach%20a%20height%20of%20about%204.6%20feet%2C%20shorter%20than%20the%20general%20average%20of%205.2%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20foray%20into%20comedy%20was%20initially%20inspired%20by%20her%20admiration%20for%20Indian%20comedians%20like%20Aditi%20Mittal%2C%20Azeem%20Banatwalla%20and%20Daniel%20Fernandes.%20She%20later%20explored%20the%20work%20of%20global%20comedians%2C%20such%20as%20Hannah%20Gadsby%2C%20Taylor%20Tomlinson%2C%20Ali%20Wong%2C%20and%20Jerry%20Seinfeld.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Sweta%20started%20with%20the%20intention%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F99756%2Findias-stuttering-comedienne-